  "original_title": "\u0bae\u0bbe\u0ba3\u0bb5\u0bb0\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bb3\u0bc1\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bc1 \u0baa\u0bc1\u0ba4\u0bbf\u0baf \u0baa\u0bb8\u0bcd\u0b9a\u0bc7\u0bb5\u0bc8",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "New bus service for students",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "The Ministry of Education has decided to start a new bus service by putting private buses into service for school students from August 1st.",
        "Also, the Ministry of Education has announced that a discussion on how to conduct schools next week will be decided on Saturday.",
        "This decision has been taken considering the current traffic problem and the increase in school transport fees.",
        "Accordingly, the Ministry of Education has informed that this new bus service will be implemented keeping in mind the school starting time and closing time to include all the schools.",
        "Fuel will be distributed through the Sri Lanka Transport Council depot to the buses used for the transportation of school students.",
        "Apart from this, the Ministry of Education has announced that steps have been taken to properly promote the bus service for students.",
        "Due to the traffic problems faced by the students and teachers, schools are conducted only 3 days a week."
      ],
